{
  "stem": "4967.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "People used to die from starvation, exhaustion, and disease.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And life carried on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "The Lithuanian who used to supply food at the black market at the cemetery stopped coming in to do dealing with the Jewish people, because it was very dangerous for them.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "The Germans realized there was something going on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "Maybe they caught a few Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "And they kept [INAUDIBLE] that there shouldn't be any dealing between the Jews and the non-Jews.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE] And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] one morning, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they put an order that everybody must report in a certain place in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "It was 5 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "And we marched there to the ghett-- to the assembly place.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "And the whole ghetto was assembled there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "And nobody went to work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "Nobody was-- was ordered to go to work.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "The Germans arrived, and they made a selection, who is going right, and who is going left.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "Who's going left, we found out afterwards, survived, remained in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "Who were going left didn't come back, was liquidated on a certain fort or in a forest or whatever it is.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] When we came to the Germans and looked at us, we showed them our papers.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And one German say to me, [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] To me, you go to the left.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "You go to the right.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "And my father and my late mother begged the Germans.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 78,
      "text": "Please, we are together.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 79,
      "text": "And my husband, here is his papers, chief electrician, electrician for the broadcasting cooperation in Kaunas.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 80,
      "text": "Whenever he used to go to work, he didn't go with a guard.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 81,
      "text": "He had a special permit to go without the guard, he and another guy.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
